.: 2005-01-01 rev.52 (ver 0.3.0)
	.- [change] users-guide and reference manual are updated
	.- [change] topping names are changed from 'xxx_xxx_xxx' to 'xxx-xxx-xxx'
	.- [change] command line option '-iN' is now deprecated
	.- [bugfix] mkmethod-php: command option '-v' prints revision and date correctly
	
.: 2004-12-31 rev.51
	.- [bugfix] KwartzAnalyzeVisitor aborts with the error 'Fatal error: Cannot access private property'
	
.: 2004-12-30 rev.50
	.- [change] indent format out output script is changed
	.- [bugfix] command-line option '-i0' is now recognized
	
.: 2004-12-30 rev.49
	.- [enhance] class KwartzJstlTranslator is divided into JSTL1.1 and JSTL1.0
	.- [enhance] common functions support for JSTL1.1 except list_new() and has_new() and hash_keys()
	.- [enhance] kwartz-php supports new directives of JSTL1.1
	
.: 2004-12-30 rev.48
	.- [enhance] common functions support for PHP and eRuby.
	
.: 2004-12-30 rev.47
	.- [bugfix] KwartzParser#parse_statement() calls parse_load_stmt()
	
.: 2004-09-23 rev.44 (ver 0.2.0) 
	.- [enhance] error reporting enhanced
	.- [enhance] @C(expr) is not escaped even when the command-line option '-s' or '-e' is specified
	.- [bugfix] 'flag?true:false' was recognized as ':' + name
	.- [bugfix] several conditional expression is correctly translated when lang is 'jsp'
	
.: 2004-09-19 (ver 0.1.0)
	.- Public Beta Release
